  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  chronic non-pulsatile tinnitus &gt; 3 months

          -  tinnitus has a clear otological cause

          -  age &gt; 18 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pulsatile tinnitus

          -  persons who take already Q10

          -  pregnancy

          -  cervical tinnitus

          -  holocranial tinnitus

          -  depression

          -  mental of neurological disorders

          -  history of chemotherapy

          -  middle ear diseases
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
